metadata.name: Clean Lucifer
metadata.description: thank you for your interest in my art, fun for me to have people stop and read the process of my work i am ron lugasi a third year design student (2022) and artist and lifelong creator father of 4 lovely children and married to galia. my "Clean Lucifer" is part of a project called NFTWANNABE that combines design and formal research of the NFT world i have created here a combination of design art and research
